 "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002189, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, send your punishment upon the sinners and destroyers, the ones who envied Your Prophet and fought against Your friends, and worshipped other than You, and reckoned the acts forbidden by You as Halal. (O Allah) curse their leaders and followers, and all those accompanied them and were deceived, then were disgraced along with them, or were content with their behaviour, curse them immensely.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Allah! Un faajiro’n ko azaab mein mubtela kar jinho’n ne Tere Rasool ki mukhaalefat ki aur Tere waliyo’n se jang ki aur (Tujhe chhod kar) Tere gair ki parastish ki, aur Teri haraam ki huwi cheezo’n ko halaal samjha. Ay Allah (baatil) rehbaro’n aur (unki) pairwi karne waalo’n ko aur jo bhi unke giroh mein se ho, jinho’n ne un se dagha-baazi ki, unke dushman ka saath diya ho, ya unke fel (amal) par raazi ho un par ziyadah se ziyadah laanat kar.", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA A’ZZE-BIL FAJARA-TAL LAZEE-NA SHA-AQ-QOO RASOOLA-KA WA HAARA-BOO AWLIYAA-A-KA WA A’BADOO GHAIRA-KA W